description: 695 E 5th Street, Unit 15 is a 1,865 SF, 3 bed, 3 bath townhome with 3 private outdoor spaces and parking. Entry opens to living room with double height ceilings and windows, dining room, kitchen, breakfast nook and walk out to balcony. Second floor features two guest bedrooms, full bathroom and a walk-in closet for linens or extra storage. Third floor features primary ensuite with closet and private balcony. Lower level features recreation space, gas fireplace, in-unit washer / dryer, ample storage and walk-out to patio with storage shed. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a move-in ready townhome with exceptional indoor-outdoor living! For real-time offer alerts or to make an offer, see Final Offer.
